RESCRIPTIVE MODEL FOR PLANNING A NATIONAL SCIENTIFIC AND TECHNICALINFORMATION SYSTEM FOR EGYPT.     (PHD THESIS-UNIVERSITY OF PITTSBURGH.) DESCRIBES A STUDY WHICH SURVEYED THEPREVAILING CONDITIONS OF THE PRESENT SYSTEM FOR HANDLING SCIENTIFIC ANDTECHNICAL INFORMATION IN EGYPT; INVESTIGATED WHETHER THERE IS A NEED FOR ANATIONAL SCIENTIFIC AND TECHNICAL INFORMATION SYSTEM; AND PROPOSED A MODEL FORTHE ESTABLISHMENT OF A NATIONAL TECHNICAL INFORMATION SYSTEM FOR EGYPT